Grounded against primary publishers (data-source-agent):
- RCB FX-reserve freeze (OFAC Directive 4, EO 14024): 2022-02-28 -> 2022q1
  (Treasury jy0612)
- EO 14114 secondary sanctions: 2023-12-22 -> 2023q4 (Federal Register)
- HFCAA CII determinations begin 2022q1 (conclusive 2022-03-30), PCAOB
  access restored 2022q4 -> bounded reg_hfcaa window (SEC/PCAOB)
- Didi/tech crackdown onset 2021q3 (SEC EDGAR CIK 1764757)
- CORRECTION surfaced: outbound-investment EO is EO 14105 (2023-08-09,
  2023q3), NOT Dec-2023; the Dec-2023 event is EO 14114 (secondary
  sanctions). Grounded against the Federal Register, not silently mapped.

Treatment panel (22 rows keyed by fiscal_quarter, merges cleanly onto the
full crosswalk panel, 0 orphans): sanc_freeze_post, sanc_eo2023_post,
sanc_intensity (CMIC additions; flagged survivorship-biased/sparse ->
INCOMPLETE, event dummies are primary), reg_hfcaa_post, reg_crackdown_post.
Measured sanctions-vs-regulatory collinearity r=0.828 (freeze vs crackdown);
